Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.36,0:00:09.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來 叫我 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.07,0:00:12.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老…老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:21.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一定是那種氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:25.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不稱呼名字 只和我玩老師play
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:27.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:30.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.57,0:00:33.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:37.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:43.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂 因為 非常地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.67,0:00:44.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,熾熱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.55,0:00:49.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的 就算是老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:55.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:17.54,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}一番大切なものを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:20.01,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}一番大切にしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:24.60,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}そんな単純なことが今は一番出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.21,0:01:27.47,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}もしも運命があるのならば　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.47,0:01:30.19,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}「あなたは運命の人」なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:35.03,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}そんな言葉今を壊しそうで言えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:37.65,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}近くに居ても遠く感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.65,0:01:40.17,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}行ったり来たりしてるこの想い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:43.18,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}諦める　諦めない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.18,0:01:45.33,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}終わらない花占い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:47.77,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}宝箱の鍵失ったなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:50.39,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}キラキラした想いて抱きしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:57.93,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}仄かに色付いた欠片をため息に隠す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:08.39,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}目が合ったなら逸らさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:10.97,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}秘められたこの嘘を見抜いてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.97,0:02:13.45,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}限界がもう分からないの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:16.24,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}だから今は何も言わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.69,0:02:23.30,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}苦しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:27.23,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}怖いほどあなたが好き
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:17.54,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}最寶貴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:20.01,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}最想要去珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:24.60,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}如此簡單的事情現在卻最無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.21,0:01:27.47,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}若是真的存在命運
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.47,0:01:30.19,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}「你就是我的命定之人」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:35.03,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}無法說出口 懼怕這些話語將會毀掉現在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:37.65,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}近在咫尺卻彷若遙不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.65,0:01:40.17,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}反覆無常的這份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:43.18,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}放棄 還是堅持
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.18,0:01:45.33,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}永無止境的花瓣占卜
