Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:50.39,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}抱緊最後一絲希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:57.93,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}將逐漸泛紅的碎片藏進一聲聲嘆息中
