Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:16.24,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}所以現在請你沉默就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.69,0:02:23.30,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}愛的如此痛苦
