Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:35.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,初體驗是很理想的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:40.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不早不晚 高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:44.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比我大兩歲 大家憧憬著的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:48.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩當然不是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:50.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像是在帶領著我的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:54.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要努力地天真爛漫地款待就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:59.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但 也說不上是款待 因為這只是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:05.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,越是如此 前輩就越是性奮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:06.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我被愛著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:10.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在充分品味到自己的價值的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:17.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩的話 就像是會憧憬著那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:20.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想將那些她們如何忌恨也無法得到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:24.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,滿滿地 滿滿地鋪上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:27.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,全部妝點好 目不轉睛地看得失神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:31.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,用手把玩著 蹂躪著 隨意使用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fad(400,0)\fs90\pos(951,777)}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:40.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 我對這之外的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:42.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一無所知……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:59.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像那樣的思春期 我沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:03.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:06.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我這人很無趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:09.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 哈 啊 呃 不 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:14.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在別人面前說自己壞話是第一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:17.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭啊 好像說了洩氣話一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:13.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}與其說是無趣 倒不如說是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:18.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}周圍的女人都無法同台競技的算計
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:24.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,超利己的甚至感覺到包容力的級別
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:29.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我想這說不定也是算計
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:32.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡 很有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:37.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:41.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 有說讓我生氣的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:43.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:49.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得我感受到了「可接受的」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:52.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有種自己被接受了的錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:56.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太天真了 那樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:05:00.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜…茜姐 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:04.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,下週 要一起出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:06.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哪也行 只要茜姐喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:09.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:14.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊抱歉 那天是給鐘井老師的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:17.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,粉碎掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,親切的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:22.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:27.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們都是同類 就算不想懂也會懂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:31.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像是無論如何都會有無法改變的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,後退一步的時機之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:35.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真傷心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:38.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭宋_GBK\fad(400,0)\fs90\pos(951,777)}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:43.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 一直都是一成不變的東西在不斷重複
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:45.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:48.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外 一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:52.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 今天明天也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭宋_GBK\bord0\fs30\c&H5D5D62&\b1\frx8\fry0\frz7.525\pos(909,267)}今天真是非常感謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭宋_GBK\bord0\fs30\c&H5D5D62&\frz6.523\pos(1017,432)\b1}真的是非常開心。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭宋_GBK\bord0\fs30\c&H5D5D62&\frz6.776\pos(981,576)\b1}下次再去吃好吃的吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭宋_GBK\bord0\fs30\c&H5D5D62&\pos(978,678)\frz6.761\b1}我也很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭宋_GBK\bord0\fs30\c&H5D5D62&\frz7.565\pos(984,828)\b1}下次也一定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.07,0:05:54.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今後也一直
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:57.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人也能好好過的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.70,0:06:02.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺變得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:11.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和茜姐做還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:14.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想想接吻的意義的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:15.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,J-POP嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:16.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}J-POP，即Japanese POP（日本的流行音樂）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:17.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,少女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:20.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 又劈腿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:22.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的快分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:25.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 但是 我喜歡他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:28.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,男人的話就算不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:31.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事也會隨便做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:33.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,劈腿也不是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:36.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:39.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊也很舒服嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:42.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老實講現在還很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛那也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:43.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}都聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:48.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 男人的感情排在性慾後面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:51.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:53.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:59.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 想幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:01.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小麥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:03.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:06.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:09.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那天是給鐘井老師的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:13.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明天 請不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:20.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為 你是更加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:23.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,聽話的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:28.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 嫉妒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:31.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:33.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:36.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人急躁 這從容
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:40.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然討厭 這不是明顯的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:42.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到底想說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:46.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 這人居然到現在也沒被人捅刀子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:48.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:50.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:02.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,生氣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:07.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,生氣了也是張漂亮的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:10.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:11.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:13.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:18.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢 討厭我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:24.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 原來如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:27.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:30.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,本能的 絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.81,0:08:32.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比不上的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:35.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 在瑟瑟發抖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:39.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不想被喜歡的人討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:45.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明天 請不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:52.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我說 感到討厭 的話？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是很喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:06.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,無法喜歡上任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:11.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,連手中收集到的好意之類的執著都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.46,0:09:19.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來都不拒 逝都不追啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:23.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣 不是非常地孤獨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:27.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:32.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還想讓像那樣的人稍稍看一下我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:34.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真愚蠢啊我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:39.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢笨拙 無藥可救
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:45.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:47.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但已經是中午了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:52.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:03.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 雖說今天是鐘井老師的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:07.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡水族館嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:13.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 啊不 我是想說皆川老師可能會喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:17.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不用顧及我啦 去鐘井老師你喜歡的地方就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:18.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:23.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說約會就這樣繼續著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:26.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是第幾次了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:29.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不怎麼記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:33.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 今天是星期六對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:37.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的 是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:41.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去看企鵝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:42.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,難以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼那之後都不去賓館了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:55.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 以前也有過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:11:00.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明顯心懷鬼胎卻不出手的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:02.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但這回不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.11,0:11:07.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}企鵝看起來那樣 實際上長著很多毛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:07.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們做過一次的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:09.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是那一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:12.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上也感覺像是我去挑逗他的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:15.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:17.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:20.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的理由其一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:24.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和我睡過一次後再也沒有要求第二次很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:24.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊 看啊 長著毛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:27.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,企鵝為什麼會這麼可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:29.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的理由其二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:32.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以這種奇怪的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:37.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已經進行了很多次健全無聊的約會這件事很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:39.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比起奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.29,0:11:44.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像已經明確覺得「討厭」的理由其三
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:50.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這更像是我在追求他的狀態是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:54.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人煩躁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:57.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已經夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:11:59.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不需要他了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:02.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉呢 安樂岡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:04.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 搬到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:05.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,膠布不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:08.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這真的來得及準備嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:15.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 果然是忘在教室裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:45.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:48.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我這邊才是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:50.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:52.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:55.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 以後就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:56.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是茜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:01.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇 又有了新男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:02.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,拓也 她是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:05.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真是喜歡玩男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:08.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:10.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:12.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也沒資格說別人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:14.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:17.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛 喂你在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要突然對別人說沒禮貌的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:20.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:23.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}跟你沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.64,0:13:26.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}怎麼 嫉妒嗎 你是嫉妒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:21.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不知為何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:25.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,或許是因為今天我特別地火大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:27.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:33.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不就是無法成為第一被我玩過就扔了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:36.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為嫉妒就在那裡磨磨唧唧糾纏不休
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:40.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為這樣才會被我甩了 懂不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:43.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴滾一邊去吧 蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.46,0:13:46.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很想這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:48.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:49.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你好煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:49.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是這種角色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不會道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:53.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:55.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:59.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙真的是個喜歡玩男人的臭婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.39,0:14:01.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:03.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:04.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:08.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,皆川老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:09.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,鐘井老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:13.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:16.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是個臭婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:20.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,攻略難度意外地低
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:22.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和誰都能睡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:25.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟冰清玉潔什麼的更沾不上邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:30.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得我不能回應鐘井老師您的任何期待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:32.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以約會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:35.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:37.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:39.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:39.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 順便一提
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:46.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為免你問出為什麼 怎麼會這種愚蠢的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:47.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我先回答你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:51.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得多情就是我的生物本能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:56.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被異性追捧讓我感覺很快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.73,0:14:57.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,與此同時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:15:02.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老實說我更喜歡挑起同性對我的嫉妒心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:07.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,話都說到這種程度了 應該不會變質為跟蹤狂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:11.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話 這種事我是無法停下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:13.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 真的再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:17.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 結束了結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:19.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,回去看幾集外國電視劇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:21.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,發發訊息給其他男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.53,0:15:25.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,疼愛一下著迷於我的高中男生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:29.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要盡快回到這樣的日常呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:34.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你不用停下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:37.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不停下來也無所謂的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:38.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:42.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的手放開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:56.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不用停下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:15:58.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:06.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我在問你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:08.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:10.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是字面上的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:13.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡被NTR？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:15.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:19.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這人的性癖比我想像的還要糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:21.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明看起來挺正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:24.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以後…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:26.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再約會了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:30.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:34.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼想都沒想就回答他了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:40.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 真的很稀奇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:42.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜姐居然主動約我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:45.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:49.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是他沒有放手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:53.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是我沒能甩開他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:58.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明至今為止我曾無數次甩手離開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:02.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 你討厭我和其他人睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:06.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 該怎麼說才是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:08.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,討…討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:10.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:12.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:16.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 說白了是因為嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:18.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:21.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂嫉妒就是來自於占有慾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:23.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:27.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜姐完全沒有過這種感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:32.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:36.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原本以為幾乎要到手的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:39.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被別人搶走的話還是會有點不甘心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:41.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:44.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這種事還沒發生過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:48.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比我想的還要像個孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:55.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,自己想聽到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:18:00.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是絕對不會從心儀的人嘴裡說出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:03.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:06.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:10.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對 所以我們聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:12.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:15.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,從並不心儀的人那裡倒是聽過許多這樣的話了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:17.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:20.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不就是優越感嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:22.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,或許是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:25.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:26.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:28.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是我逼她說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:33.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再將這樣的她用作沉浸於感傷時的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:34.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一個如此差勁的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:37.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一個沉醉於此 更加差勁的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:41.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一個無法徹底拋下那樣的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:45.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有勇氣開始一段新人生的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:49.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為對這樣的自己還有莫名的留戀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:55.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為非常非常非常非常非常地害怕改變
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.77,0:19:01.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還是有人不顧一切地一直愛著我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:05.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的我 必須做出改變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.44,0:19:08.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:11.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要真想改變別人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,首先得改變自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:17.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,察覺得太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:21.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不錯啊 總比察覺不到要好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:23.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:25.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:27.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為了改變自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:31.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有些東西無論如何都得放手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:33.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比如熟悉的聲音 氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:37.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,儘管如此 我卻遲遲不肯放手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:40.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使在夢中我也不肯認清這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要依賴到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:44.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這最後的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:47.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,執著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:57.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:19:59.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,睡得真熟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:01.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為年輕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:09.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 我正在打分數呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:12.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:13.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:15.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和你約會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:20.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:22.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這條界線
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:24.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能待會再說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:27.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正兰亭宋_GBK\fs75\frz270\fad(400,0)\pos(1086,564)}不拖拉的。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:27.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不會退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:30.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,時機氣氛什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:31.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不會管的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:34.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:37.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我還年輕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:39.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我裝得一本正經
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:40.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,裝作我們是對等的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:42.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但其實我還是幼稚到不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:43.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事我無法下定決心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:45.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也懶得去下定決心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:46.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:49.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:51.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,遜斃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:53.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,黑歷史確定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:55.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:59.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我從來沒有心跳得這麼快過
